                  <span>NAP consistency across directories</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex gap-2 items-start">
                  <span class="text-[#32C55F]">→</span>
                  <span>Local citation building</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex gap-2 items-start">
                  <span class="text-[#32C55F]">→</span>
                  <span>Location-specific landing pages</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex gap-2 items-start">
                  <span class="text-[#32C55F]">→</span>
                  <span>Service area optimization</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex gap-2 items-start">
                  <span class="text-[#32C55F]">→</span>
                  <span>Competitor analysis</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- On-Page Optimization -->
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
            <div class="h-1 bg-rebel-green"></div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">On-Page Optimization</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                <li class="flex gap-2 items-start">
                  <span class="text-[#32C55F]">→</span>
                  <span>Title and meta description optimization</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex gap-2 items-start">
                  <span class="text-[#32C55F]">→</span>
                  <span>Header structure and keyword placement</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex gap-2 items-start">
